# Blueprints

Blueprints used in v0.1.0

## for Factory

Self-expansion factory uses following blueprints.
The blueprints must be contains in the same container and exact order.

![Blueprints](files/blueprints.png)


### Target Blueprint

It's an empty blueprint(but doesn't have to be empty) that is used for finding the container that contains following blueprints.
This blueprint must be named `__init__`.

[source](https://github.com/mitsuyoshi-yamazaki/BlindFactoryBuilder/blob/v0.0.1/control.lua#L59)
